You are working on a React + TypeScript analytics platform (ChillView) using Tailwind CSS and Apache ECharts.

The app already supports an Org Chart (tree chart), but it is currently embedded inside a dashboard and is hard to explore due to space and density issues.

Your task is to build a **full-page Org Chart Explore view** with modern UI/UX similar to Power BI Focus Mode or OrgVue.

---

# 🎯 GOAL

Create a dedicated page `/org-chart` that provides:

1. Full-screen org chart visualization
2. Search and highlight functionality
3. Zoom and pan controls
4. Expand/collapse controls
5. Filters (Department, Location, Role)
6. Breadcrumb navigation
7. Clean layout and spacing

---

